---
title: "Call for paper"
---

<div class="row" data-equalizer>
  <div class="large-6 columns">
    <div class="panel" data-equalizer-watch>
      <h2>Deadline: 28 August 2015</h2>

      <p>
      We invite abstracts for papers covering any topic related to food and
      nutrition in Europe including, but not limited to, the following:
      </p>

      <ul>
        <li>
          The development of policy by humanitarian, governmental and intergovernmental organisations.
        </li>

        <li> The relationship between diet, nutrition and health.  </li>

        <li>
          Economic, anthropomorphic and statistical approaches to the analysis of
  food consumption.
        </li>

        <li>
          Household-level analysis of nutrition/food expenditure and living standards.
        </li>

        <li>
          Transnational comparisons between European countries and/or studies
          of change over time in one country or region.
        </li>
      </ul>

      <p>
This conference is open to early career and established academics in any
relevant discipline. The conference will be organised on workshop principles
in one venue.
      </p>

    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="large-6 columns">
    <form class="panel" data-equalizer-watch>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="large-12 columns">
          <label>
            Academic title
            <input name="academic_title" type="text" placeholder="" />
          </label>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="large-6 columns">
          <label>
            First name
            <input name="first_name" type="text" placeholder="" />
          </label>
        </div>
        <div class="large-6 columns">
          <label>
            Surname
            <input name="surname" type="text" placeholder="" />
          </label>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="large-6 columns">
          <label>
            Email
            <input name="email" type="email" placeholder="@" />
          </label>
        </div>
        <div class="large-6 columns">
          <label>
            Affiliated University
            <input type="text" placeholder="" />
          </label>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <fieldset>
          <p>Abstracts of 300 words, for papers of 20 minutes.</p>
          <label>
            Upload proposal
            <input name="paper" type="file" accept="application/*" value="Add document" />
          </label>
        </fieldset>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="large-12 columns">
          <p>Decisions on the conference program will be made in September 2015.</p>
          <button type="submit" class="small radius button">Submit</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </form>
  </div>
</div>
